## Pre-Publish Checklist

Before publishing, verify:

- [ ] Headline includes primary keyword
- [ ] Title tag under 60 characters
- [ ] Meta description under 105 characters
- [ ] URL slug is short and clear
- [ ] Primary keyword in first 100 words
- [ ] All images have alt text
- [ ] Maximum 2 images used
- [ ] All code in proper code boxes
- [ ] Internal links added where relevant
- [ ] FAQ section included (3-5 questions)
- [ ] Conclusion has clear CTA/next step
- [ ] Proofread for clarity and errors

